te>可唔可以收細佬做𡃁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以"},{"pid":"46578f601b1fcf32e42cb30328b24f3d64be168e","tid":291052,"uid":124112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:29:43.000Z","msg":"你就想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982e6f99d55a530019a5ca8bcbcda3ed6d2740b6","tid":291052,"uid":6507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"點解唔報HA既HD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea1de05e5e1d932f3dddfa398c7e05b7d735021","tid":291052,"uid":124112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔報HA既HD?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無full cert"},{"pid":"4f58a6cacf7242b597b2394fa0113da8ccc8ce2e","tid":291052,"uid":101341,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:53:29.000Z","msg":"搭小巴去恆管<br />\n<br />\n是咁的 <br />\n尋日約曬成班以前中學同學出黎聚下舊，食下飯咁<br />\n本來過程都幾輕鬆愉快既 <br />\n但係突然呢，有一個升左恆大既中學同學就提議玩下遊戲咁，廢事咁悶 <br />\n當中有人就提議玩下D數字遊戲啦，計下數咁 <br />\n大家都話好既，當係玩下啦 <br />\n<br />\n咁就一直計啦，突然間有一鋪 <br />\n我唔小心咁將好簡單既加數計錯左，將10+7+9+5，計左做32，比正確答案多左一 <br />\n我D FD就笑我話我咁渣嫁，我都唔好意思咁笑左幾下 <br />\n就係依個時候，讀恆大果個FD就話我:「咁渣嫁，中學生WO。」 <br />\n由於小弟不材，升唔到上大學，要係下年進行自修<br />\n我當時就無聲出，因為知道恆大係一間好勁既新晉大學， <br />\n所以只可以細細聲同佢講番:「唔好意思囉，大學生。」 <br />\n<br />\n但由於我條氣好唔順，所以決定係聽日去佢果間恆大到搵佢再玩過隻GAME <br />\n由於我住九龍果邊，唔係好熟新界﹗路 <br />\n<br />\n上左小巴，途中見到有數棟好有霸氣既建築物，坐立係山與屋村中間，旁邊仲有幾個工地作為點綴，幾個地盤佬企係街邊，左手撩住鼻屎，右手抓下屎忽。 <br />\n<br />\n我心諗，依一間一定就係傳說中既恆大 <br />\n<br />\n由於我坐係車尾。迫使我一定要運用我豪壯既聲音大叫出我既目的地 <br />\n<br />\n「恆大有落唔該。」 <br />\n<br />\n講完之後仲要撥下頭髮，電一電側邊D女 <br />\n諗住可以靠下「恆大」既威名，去型一陣，溝下女<br />\n點知個小巴司機又好大聲咁回應我:「恆咩Q大啊，恆管就有。」 <br />\n係依個時侯，車上引出一陣爆笑 <br />\n坐係我側邊個中學妹都引唔住笑左我一陣 <br />\n<br />\n我都唔等佢停車，即刻係個車窗到跳左出去 <br />\n<br />\n我跑入恆大，即刻搵我個FD對質 <br />\n我問佢:「依間唔係恆大咩?做咩我岩岩落車嗌恆大會被人笑。」 <br />\n我個FD聽到我咁樣講，面都紅埋咁答我:「關唔關你事啊。」"},{"pid":"4d3bcf31e259b05bdbee5d25f557fc0e59a2449a","tid":291052,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"收到東華HD Nursing confitional offer<br />\n要15分"},{"pid":"9c8fda6d5689089ebf551617f361bfbb5a73792b","tid":291052,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"脫貧嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f0ee386a9b604554c971a49fbbac54b3439cee","tid":291052,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"窮廢撚向上流動嘅唯一選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b06d94d84a8dd65c7d16e6b0a26ab92c86f341","tid":291052,"uid":48571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"上年我in完，去到放榜前一晚先有offer"},{"pid":"16d8519cc38783f44ab1d3632232cc89af84024f","tid":291052,"uid":454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收到東華HD Nursing confitional offer<br />\n要15分</blockquote><br />\n咁撚廢個condition<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff934bea40a0ca635cbbef0c043d01de0356fb7","tid":291052,"uid":6507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:45